# Copy to services.yaml and replace all API keys/tokens with real values.
# This file is gitignored because it contains live API keys and tokens.
#
# Tokens needed:
#   - Home Assistant: Long-lived access token from HA profile page
#   - Immich: API key from Immich user settings
#   - Kopia: Web UI password (KOPIA_PASS from .env)
#   - Outline: API token from Outline settings
#   - Mealie: Long-lived API token from Mealie user profile
#   - Plex: Token from any Plex API call (https://www.plexopedia.com/plex-media-server/api/server/token/)
#   - UniFi: Local API key from UniFi Network settings
#
# See https://gethomepage.dev/widgets/ for widget configuration docs.
